  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The Purpose of this study was to evaluate the effect of the combination glimepiride/metformin
      over endothelial dysfunction (ED) in asymptomatic patients with type 2 diabetes mellitus (DM)
      using 13N-ammonia-positron emission tomography (PET).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
