  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Both genders

          -  At least 18 years old

          -  Type 2 diabetes mellitus diagnosis

          -  Signed Informed Consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  History of smoking, hypertension, dyslipidemia, ischemic heart disease or autoimmune
             rheumatic diseases

          -  Pregnancy or lactation

          -  History of abuse and/or substance dependence within 6 months preceding the survey.

          -  History of glimepiride or metformin allergy
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
